Osool Database Migrations
=========================

This directory contains Alembic migrations for the Osool platform.

## Creating a New Migration

After modifying models in `app/models.py`, generate a new migration:

```bash
cd backend
alembic revision --autogenerate -m "Description of changes"
```

## Applying Migrations

To upgrade to the latest version:

```bash
alembic upgrade head
```

To downgrade one version:

```bash
alembic downgrade -1
```

## Viewing Migration History

```bash
alembic history
alembic current
```

## Production Deployment

Migrations are automatically applied on container startup via the entrypoint script.
